$ Examples for Visual Basic for Application accessing the Windows API: Bring window to the top

This example uses → development/languages/VBA/Win-API/examples/EnumWindows[`EnumWindows`] to find a window by its caption and then
calls `ShowWindow` and `SetForeGroundWindow` to bring it to the top.

This example example needs the VBA declarations of the Windows API which can be found
→ development/languages/VBA/Win-API[here].
 
gh|WinAPI-4-VBA|/examples/BringWindowToTop.bas||

